1
00:00:00,250 --> 00:00:01,880
Let's go.

2
00:00:05,630 --> 00:00:07,340
Shiono-san.

3
00:00:08,470 --> 00:00:10,260
Will you work with me?

4
00:00:11,510 --> 00:00:13,010
On what?

5
00:00:13,220 --> 00:00:15,060
If you break up, this will all blow over.

6
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:18,140
If a scandal breaks now, you're finished.

7
00:00:18,690 --> 00:00:20,020
Whether it's Makoto

8
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:21,440
or you.

9
00:00:21,650 --> 00:00:24,650
I've seen too many people ruin their own careers.

10
00:00:25,940 --> 00:00:28,490
I don't want you two to follow in their footsteps.

11
00:00:28,490 --> 00:00:31,450
Once you've made it, then you can...

12
00:00:31,450 --> 00:00:33,280
I can't do that.

13
00:00:34,660 --> 00:00:36,330
Shiono-san.

14
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:39,710
I know you're looking out for me.

15
00:00:39,710 --> 00:00:42,040
I really do.

16
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:48,590
But...

17
00:00:49,800 --> 00:00:52,090
Without Yuki,

18
00:00:53,390 --> 00:00:56,600
I would never have been noticed.

19
00:00:59,230 --> 00:01:01,600
Sigh...

20
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:04,400
Makoto needs Yuki.

21
00:01:04,940 --> 00:01:07,190
The only one who can make Makoto shine...

22
00:01:07,190 --> 00:01:09,110
is Yuki.

23
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:15,490
I see.

24
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:20,620
I'm sorry, Makoto.

25
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:24,170
As your manager,
maybe I didn't understand you well enough.

26
00:01:27,460 --> 00:01:29,460
Shiono-san.

27
00:01:31,930 --> 00:01:34,340
I'll do everything I can to support Makoto.

28
00:01:36,850 --> 00:01:39,560
Please, help us.

29
00:01:40,730 --> 00:01:43,730
We need your help.

30
00:01:46,860 --> 00:01:49,110
Please.

31
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:23,020
(We only made it to today
because of that day...)

32
00:02:23,020 --> 00:02:24,890
(Yuki made a suggestion.)

33
00:02:30,150 --> 00:02:31,320
Are you ready?

34
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,490
(Today is our anniversary.)

35
00:02:32,940 --> 00:02:35,780
(I got us cruise tickets as a gift.)

36
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:37,120
(A private cabin, of course.)

37
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,780
(And I have another present planned.)

38
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:42,000
Wait, how does this work?

39
00:02:43,750 --> 00:02:44,750
What are you doing?

40
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:47,330
My tie...

41
00:02:48,380 --> 00:02:49,380
I don't know how to tie it.

42
00:02:49,380 --> 00:02:51,090
Oh, honestly...

43
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,340
Give it here.

44
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:00,640
Okay.

45
00:03:01,100 --> 00:03:02,600
Thanks.

46
00:03:04,350 --> 00:03:05,850
Hmm?

47
00:03:06,350 --> 00:03:07,600
Hmm?

48
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,150
Just as I thought...

49
00:03:11,150 --> 00:03:13,070
You look best in the makeup I do.

50
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,700
I know.

51
00:03:21,370 --> 00:03:22,990
Shall we go, Princess?

52
00:03:23,450 --> 00:03:25,790
Huh? I'm the princess?

53
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:30,500
We're two princes.

54
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:32,130
That's so embarrassing.

55
00:03:32,210 --> 00:03:33,460
Hahaha.

56
00:03:57,280 --> 00:04:02,000
To everyone watching Season 2,

57
00:04:02,740 --> 00:04:05,750
thank you from the bottom of our hearts.

58
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:10,250
Thanks to you,
the team was able to come together again.

59
00:04:10,250 --> 00:04:14,000
Thank you so much for making
Season 2 possible.

60
00:04:14,710 --> 00:04:18,260
Wow, it's finally over.
I'm a bit sad to see it end.

61
00:04:18,260 --> 00:04:19,970
Me too.

62
00:04:19,970 --> 00:04:21,430
But we have some good news!

63
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,680
Wow!

64
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:27,560
Coming up next for Season 2...

65
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:30,270
A special episode is coming soon!

66
00:04:31,850 --> 00:04:35,940
With exclusive interviews and behind-the-scenes footage,
you won't want to miss it!

67
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:38,400
Make sure to tune in!
